ta.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/111%2c%e6%99%ba%e7%b0%a1%2c38%2c20220930%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,111,智簡,38,20220930,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"智簡","JNO":"38","JDATE":"20220930","JTITLE":"違反商標法"}